## **6. CHANGELOG.md**
```markdown
# Changelog

## [0.1.0] - 2025-09-27
### Added
- Initial release of `AnimatedCounterX`.
- Supports start and end values.
- Increment (count up) and decrement (count down) mode.
- Supports both int and double.
- Custom duration, text style, and decimal precision.
